===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# [[practical|Practical]], concerned with making [[decision]]s and [[action]]s that are [[useful]] in [[practice]], [[not]] just [[theory]]
#: ''The sturdy furniture in the student lounge was '''pragmatic''', but unattractive.''

